0:01:57.200,0:02:02.100
Zita rangu ndi Danielle Amy uye ndinobva kuAustralia.

0:02:02.100,0:02:06.760
Murume ari parutivi rwangu murume wangu akanakisa Trevor.

0:02:06.760,0:02:07.980
Takungamuchirai mese muri vaviri.

0:02:07.980,0:02:13.380
Kwese uko kwamabva ku Australia - zvokwadi mabva kurefu.

0:02:13.380,0:02:16.020
Mweya Mutsvene ndiye anopa mubayiro.

0:02:16.020,0:02:18.760
Wanunurwa sezvo taona pasikirini.

0:02:18.760,0:02:23.640
Tinoda kunzwa kubva kwauri kuti mweya yakaipa iyoyo yange ichikukanganisa sei mupenyu hwako.

0:02:23.640,0:02:28.100
Ndapota, enda mberi neuchapupu hwako.

0:02:28.100,0:02:33.420
Chakandiudza pa SCOAN chaiva chekuti

0:02:33.420,0:02:36.960
Ndakanga ndi chitambura noutano hwangu uye ndakawanikwa ndiine

0:02:36.960,0:02:43.580
zvirwere zvakawanda zvisingarapike.

0:02:43.580,0:02:50.960
nhengo dzemhuri yangu dzirikurwara chaizvo ndakanga ndichivatarisa.

0:02:50.960,0:02:57.440
Ndakava nerudaviro rwekuti Mwari akanga aine zvakawanda zvangu pamwe nemhuri yangu.

0:02:57.440,0:03:01.000
uye ini handaizotora"kwete" se mhinduro.

0:03:01.000,0:03:08.240
Takanyora rukumbiro rwe kuti tiuye ku SCOAN kuzogamuchira kuporeswa ne kununurwa.

0:03:08.240,0:03:13.220
Sisi wedu ataura kuti akauya kwete chete nokuda kwekurwisa nezvakaipa kwaive akatarisana nako

0:03:13.220,0:03:18.420
asi nekudawo kwekuti akanga aine zvimwe zvirwere zvemadyiro ake pamwe nekuve ne chisimbwa chaikanganisa hupenyu hwake.

0:03:18.420,0:03:24.300
Ndapota enda mberi nekutizivisa kuti matambudziko aya akakukanganisa sei.

0:03:24.300,0:03:27.020
Autoimmune zvinoreva kuti muviri urikuzvirwisa wega.

0:03:27.020,0:03:33.400
Nguva nenguva ndaiwanikwa ndiine matambudziko ezvirwere zvakasiyana mukati me muviri wangu

0:03:33.400,0:03:37.980
nekuti muviri wangu wairamba uchizvirwisa munzvimbo dzakasiyana.

0:03:37.980,0:03:40.340
Zvainetesa.

0:03:40.340,0:03:52.100
Ndaipedza nguva yangu zhinji ndiri ndoga kana pamubhedha nokuti ndaigara ndakaneta zvakanyanyisa.

0:03:52.100,0:03:54.820
Ishe vakandiporesa.

0:03:54.820,0:04:02.660
Kubva kununurwa nekuporeswa kwandakaitwa, handina kutora chero mishonga yandaisinwa zuva nezuva.

0:04:02.660,0:04:06.220
Ndiri kunzwa zvirinani chaizvo, ndine simba rakawedzerwa.

0:04:06.220,0:04:11.300
Ngatiisei maoko edu kuna Jesu!

0:04:11.300,0:04:15.660
Wati wakanga uine zvinetso zvakasiyana pamusoro pe utano hwako

0:04:15.660,0:04:20.840
asi zvakanga zviri nekuda kwekurwiswa nezvakaipa kwaive wakatarisana nako.

0:04:20.840,0:04:25.800
Wati wakaenda kunana chiremba uye kuti vakaramba vachikubata uine zvirwere zvakasiyana siyana.

0:04:25.800,0:04:32.720
Ungatsanangura zvakawanda pamusoro pekurwisa kwakaipa kwawakasangana nako uye kuti zvakakukanganisa sei?

0:04:32.720,0:04:34.740
Ndakanga ndiri pakurwisa nezvakaipa.

0:04:34.740,0:04:41.960
Kekutanga kandinorangarira ndeapo pandaive nemakore mashanu kana matanhatu ekuberekwa.

0:04:41.960,0:04:52.060
Ndanga ndichitambudzwa nazvo hupenyu hwangu hwose - muzviroto kana mu zviratidzo asi kakawanda panyama.

0:04:52.060,0:05:03.340
Dzimwe nguva, ndaimuka kubva ku hope dzangu ndozviona ndiine mavanga uye kumarwa marwa pamutsipa wangu.

0:05:03.340,0:05:15.180
Ndaizviona ndiine kurumwa rumwa pamuviri wangu munzvimbo dzekuti handaikwanisa kudzisvikira ndega.

0:05:15.180,0:05:19.060
Ndaive ne mavanga ne rumaradzuro muviri wangu wese.

0:05:19.060,0:05:30.600
Ndaiona mweya yakaipa ichiuya kwandiri kuzondishanyira nekutaura neni ndakamuka saizvozvi.

0:05:30.600,0:05:36.340
Zvakanaka. Wati apo waimuka,waiona panyama muine mavanga uye rumaranzuro pamuviri wenyu

0:05:36.340,0:05:39.300
munzvimbo dzawanga usingagone kusvikira wega

0:05:39.300,0:05:44.040
kukuzivisa kuti pane chimwe chinhu chakanga chaita zvinhu izvi.

0:05:44.040,0:05:45.800
Hongu, ichokwadi.

0:05:45.800,0:05:50.740
Wakambotsanangura zvinhu izvi kunana chiremba kuAustralia here?

0:05:50.740,0:05:52.220
Kwete.

0:05:52.220,0:05:55.620
Chaizvoizvo ndainzwa kunyara zvikuru uye ndaive ndega ndega.

0:05:55.620,0:05:59.160
Kune vanhu vashoma chaizvo vandaigoverana navo izvi

0:05:59.160,0:06:07.200
nekuti ndinofunga patsika,zvakasiyana kwazvo neku Australia.

0:06:07.200,0:06:14.780
Dai ndakataurira chiremba kuti mavanga kana kumwe kukuvara kwandaive ndinako,

0:06:14.780,0:06:18.100
izvo zvakaita kuti ndichengetwe muchipatara,

0:06:18.100,0:06:24.840
Ndaitya kuti ndaizochengetedzwa sebedzi nokuti vaizofunga kuti ndarasa pfungwa.

0:06:24.840,0:06:29.280
Ko wakatsanangura zvinhu izvi ku murume wako?

0:06:29.280,0:06:34.380
Hongu, ndakamuudza asi akabva atanga kusangana nazvo pachake.

0:06:34.380,0:06:38.940
Aiva chapupu pashure pekuroorana.

0:06:38.940,0:06:43.300
wati waizviona panyama, kwete kuhope chete.

0:06:43.300,0:06:48.880
Unogona kutipa muenzaniso wepazvakaitika kwauri?

0:06:48.880,0:06:54.000
Paiva ne umwe usiku mushure mekuroorana kwedu.

0:06:54.000,0:06:58.360
Ndaisakwanisa kubatwa nehope saka ndakaenda kune umwe mupanda kuno rara.

0:06:58.360,0:07:02.000
Ndakabatwa nehope ndokurota.

0:07:02.000,0:07:09.640
Paiva nevanhu vatatu vamire mukamuri yangu vaitaurirana pamusoro pekuti ndaizofa sei.

0:07:09.640,0:07:17.240
Ndaizopinda mutsaona yemotokari asi haisi tsaona yemotokari yaizondiuraya -

0:07:17.240,0:07:22.920
kwaizove kudambuka kwe tsinga kwaizondiuraya.

0:07:22.920,0:07:36.460
Ndakapepuka kubva ku hope nekuti ndakanzwa kutaura, ndakaona panyama vanhu vatatu vamire pamberi pangu.

0:07:36.460,0:07:39.920
Unogona tsanangura kuti chii chawakaona chimire pamberi penyu?

0:07:39.920,0:07:44.720
Vaiva vakareba uye varivatema pachitarisiko.

0:07:44.720,0:07:53.520
Ndakaona sekuvaima kwe girini kuita sekunge vaiva vakapfeka majazi egirini kana kuti mabhachi,kunyange makange muine rima mukamuri.

0:07:53.520,0:07:55.340
Mukamuri maitonhora kwazvo.

0:07:55.340,0:07:57.020
Ndakangonzwa ...

0:07:57.020,0:08:00.540
Hapana imwe nzira yekuzvitsanangura nayo - rwaigove rufu.

0:08:00.540,0:08:06.520
Danielle Amy Ne Murume wake - Chapupu cheRununuro

0:08:06.520,0:08:09.480
Ndakadana murume wangu.

0:08:09.480,0:08:17.040
Akapinda ndokuti paiva nechimwe chinhu chakaipa, ndisati ndambomuudza zvaive zvaitika.

0:08:17.040,0:08:18.760
Takatanga kunamata.

0:08:18.760,0:08:25.520
Takasimuka ndokuenda kukamuri yekudyira

0:08:25.520,0:08:26.940
Taive nebhegi hombe remabhuku.

0:08:26.940,0:08:33.100
Pamusoro pebhegi remabhuku paive namakanduru akawanda.

0:08:33.100,0:08:38.300
Imwechete yema kanduru yaive yatorwa ndokuiswa pabhenji remukichini.

0:08:38.300,0:08:42.440
Moto we girini waipfuta mukanduru iyoyo.

0:08:42.440,0:08:45.340
Hapana akange ambobata kanduru iyi murume wangu kana ini.

0:08:45.340,0:08:48.660
Hapana akanga aburutsa kanduru iyi pasi kana kuibatidza.

0:08:48.660,0:08:52.620
Takanzwa kuvapo kwakaipa mukati memba.

0:08:52.620,0:08:56.880
Wataura kare kuti paive nevanhu vatatu vakanga vakamira ipapo

0:08:56.880,0:09:01.000
uye wakanzwa  kukurukura kwavo kwe hurongwa hwekukuuraya

0:09:01.000,0:09:04.560
asi murume wako akapinda mukamuri akati pane chimwe chinhu chakanga chisina kunaka.

0:09:04.560,0:09:07.960
Akaonawo vanhu ava panguva iyoyo?

0:09:07.960,0:09:12.040
Kwete, haana.

0:09:12.040,0:09:16.880
Tapedza kunyengetera pamwe chete,takadzokera kunorara pamwe chete.

0:09:16.880,0:09:20.260
Ndakanga ndakara ndasvinura.

0:09:20.260,0:09:23.040
Murume wangu akotsira.

0:09:23.040,0:09:32.100
Ndakarara ipapo kudaro, munhu uyu akauya nechepamusoro pangu ndokuridza mhere nechisimba pachiso changu.

0:09:32.100,0:09:38.500
murume wangu akamuka pahope dzake, achitsiura muzita raJesu.

0:09:38.500,0:09:45.460
Akatendeukira kwandiri achirondedzera zvaakanga achangobva kuona,zvakanga zvangobva kuiitika pakurota kwake.

0:09:45.460,0:09:55.460
