0:09:55.460,0:10:00.360
Zvaukaona panyama; dhimoni richishevedzera pamusoro pe musoro wako -

0:10:00.360,0:10:08.180
murume wako akazviona zvichiitika zvakare, apo akanga akarara asi akamuka achitsiura dhimoni iri muzita raJesu?

0:10:08.180,0:10:09.840
Hongu, ichokwadi.

0:10:09.840,0:10:12.680
Chii chakaitika mushure maizvozvo?

0:10:12.680,0:10:17.440
Panguva iyoyo ndakange ndisinga shande nokuti ndakange ndisinganzwe zvakanaka

