Ndaive neshamwari yakange isinganzwe zvakanaka uye ndaina kumubikira iye nemhuri yake.

0:10:23.680,0:10:29.600
Ndakabika chekudya ndikaisa mumota kuti ndiende.

0:10:29.600,0:10:35.160
Apo ndakanga ndirikutyaira, ndakaenda kunoti ndipote mumugwagwa we kumba kwake.

0:10:35.160,0:10:45.760
Kubva kusingazivakanwe, motokari yakauya ichindirova nekuparadza motokari yandaive.

0:10:45.760,0:10:54.340
Ndakarovera musoro wangu uye ndakakuvara mutsipa wangu asi ndakanga ndisingadi kuenda kuchipatara saka ndakaenda kumba.

0:10:54.340,0:10:58.820
Murume wangu akauya kumba kuti ave neni.

0:10:58.820,0:11:03.160
Apo ndakanga ndirere pasofa, nekuti ndaiva mumarwadzo,

0:11:03.160,0:11:08.820
chimwe chinenge ingwe chakauya chikandiruma pamutsipa.

0:11:08.820,0:11:12.640
Ndaive ne marwadzo makuru kwazvo uye ndakange ndisingakwanise kupfakanyika.

0:11:12.640,0:11:20.020
moyo wangu waive usinga rove zvakanaka uye ndakanga ndiine marwadzo aidzika neruoko rwangu.

0:11:20.020,0:11:25.360
Ndaka chengetwa muchipatara zve chimbichimbi.

0:11:25.360,0:11:26.580
Zvakanaka, ndine urombo

0:11:26.580,0:11:30.380
Tinoda kuti tiwane rujekeso kubva kwauri.

0:11:30.380,0:11:34.960
Wati pashure pekusangana nechinhu chinoshamisa zuva iroro,

0:11:34.960,0:11:43.420
kuteerera vaipi vachitsanangura hurongwa hweku kuuraya mutsaona yemotokari,

0:11:43.420,0:11:49.160
zuva rimwe chete iroro, apo waive mumotokari yako uri munzira yekunosiya zvokudya ku shamwari yairwara,

0:11:49.160,0:11:51.680
wakapinda mutsaona yemota

0:11:51.680,0:11:56.040
Wakaenda kumba uye wati ingwe yakauya ikakuruma mutsipa wako.

0:11:56.040,0:12:04.760
Wainge wakakotsira here nguva iyo wakaona ingwe ichiuya kana kuti wakazviona panyama?

0:12:04.760,0:12:06.380
Hongu,zvakanga zviri panyama.

0:12:06.380,0:12:09.860
Ndakanga ndisina kukotsira.

0:12:09.860,0:12:10.460
Hongu.

0:12:10.460,0:12:17.160
Nzira chete yekuzvitsanangura nayo ndeye kuti zvakafanana nekuti pane moto uye pane utsi -

0:12:17.160,0:12:24.660
zvakanga zvakafanana huremu hwacho nekutarisika kwacho asi zvakajeka chaizvo uye nemavara aivapo.

0:12:24.660,0:12:27.260
Yakauya ikandiruma.

0:12:27.260,0:12:30.680
Saka, ingwe iyi yakauya kwauri panyama ikapinda umo waive here?

0:12:30.680,0:12:33.880
Hongu, yakauya.

0:12:33.880,0:12:39.100
Chii chakaitika pashure pekunge waenda kuchipatara?

0:12:39.100,0:12:44.320
Ndakapihwa mubhedha muchipatara kwe mazuva mashanu munzvimbo yevanorwarisa.

0:12:44.320,0:12:49.260
Vakatadza kuziva kuti dambudziko raiva rei.

0:12:49.260,0:12:58.320
Ndaive mumarwadzo akaipa ndisingakwanisi kubva pamubhedha kuenda kuchimbuzi, kana chero chinhu.

0:12:58.320,0:13:07.900
Havana kugona kuderedza marwadzo saka zvetsaona vakandikanganisira nekundipa mushonga wakawandisa pakuedza kupedza marwadzo

0:13:07.900,0:13:14.840
Ndakapedzisira ndaoma mutezo ndisisazive zvaitika kwenguva.

0:13:14.840,0:13:21.100
Izvozvo zvisati zvaitika, apo pandaipihwa imwe jekiseni,

0:13:21.100,0:13:26.940
zvakare, ndakaona ingwe ichiuya ikandiruma

0:13:26.940,0:13:34.280
Vakazongopedzisira, vaita MRI sikani.

0:13:34.280,0:13:40.180
Vakawana kuti tsandanyama yakatenderedza tsinga ne mutsipa yakanga yakadzvanywa.

0:13:40.180,0:13:44.680
Vaiva vachitya kuti zvaizokonzera sitiroko.

0:13:44.680,0:13:49.940
Havana kugona kuwana kuti chii chaikonzeresa.

0:13:49.940,0:13:54.060
Vana chiremba vakatadza kunzwisisa kuti chii chaiitika kwauri.

0:13:54.060,0:13:59.640
Wati vakakupa mishonga yakawandisa zvokuti muviri wako wakange usisagone kuita kana chinhu

0:13:59.640,0:14:02.820
