0:14:21.700,0:14:28.480
Saka, pachinhanho ichocho wakaziva kuti dambudziko rako radarika ruzivo rwevanhu, rwadarika ruzivo rwepanyama?

0:14:28.480,0:14:29.400
Hongu.

