Ndakaziva zvaive zve mweya.

0:14:32.540,0:14:36.040
Ndaizviziva hupenyu hwangu hwese kuti ndezvemweya

0:14:36.040,0:14:40.640
Ndakange ndagumirwa nekuda kuwana rusununguko.

